title: Les Snead looking for "win-win solution" on Puka Nacua extension

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Les Snead looking for "win-win solution" on Puka Nacua extension
sources.description: The Rams took care of one item on their offseason to-do list by signing head coach Sean McVay and General Manager Les Snead to contract extensions, and Snead is now moving on to other things on the agenda.
